ComicInfo.Summary: At nearly 500 pages, the hit western webcomic, Plume, comes to an end! Collecting volumes 1-4, the Omnibus tells the entire saga of Vesper Grey and her supernatural (and reluctant) guardian Corrick in the Old West. On their way to recover some stolen artifacts, they start to learn the gritty truth about the past and how far they're willing to go to avenge it. K. Lynn Smith's magnum opus has arrived!
